## Priority Fixes

1. **Immediate**: Enable CSP (#6) and restrict `read_env_file`/`write_env_file` (#10) — these are the highest-impact changes with the least effort.
2. **Short-term**: Fix auto-unlock validation (#8), hash audit log keys (#9), add password policy (#12).
3. **Medium-term**: Fix modular bias (#7), reconsider keyring strategy (#13), add file permissions (#14), evaluate command injection surface (#11).
